        You cannot win this
        game by luck.      

00:02:21.300 --> 00:02:24.050
        You have to do analysis.
              

00:02:24.050 --> 00:02:28.100
        It's careful planning and
        execution that wins this game.      

00:02:28.100 --> 00:02:32.180
        WILL HARREL: It was great to win
        this, and I just feel like      

00:02:32.180 --> 00:02:34.430
        all of our efforts have been
